<br>
There is no 'specialization check'. Spec saves you a fixed amount based on your skill every time. I don't remember the exact number at the moment though. It is around 12% or so at 200.<br>
<br>
SCM also saves a fixed amount based on what level you have. Roughly 2%,6%,12% (numbers from memory and my be off a bit). That is on every single spell you cast regardless of type. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:medium;">Zyphyr Runnersbane</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
